{
  "stem": "16395.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember the rabbi's name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my mother used to go with me Saturdays, used to take me to the-- to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother was well educated in Yiddish and in Polish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and it was very seldom in Europe that the people were educated in that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother used to sit in the middle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, now, I remember the thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Bais Yaakov, I went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, it came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she sat in the middle with the [YIDDISH], they called it in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all the women were sitting around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I sat on her knees.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was davening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "An older woman was sitting here crying, and I hated it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really didn't want to see my mother crying and all the other women crying.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she took me for a while until I grow up a little older, and I didn't want to go anymore.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because if you know what you're saying, you pray to God, they should be healthy, they should marry all of their children and have some money, you know-- and people were very religious years ago, not religious what it was good for them, but really religious.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They fanatic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They believed in it-- what they were saying, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The war was already in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother used to go every day-- not every day, every second day-- to stay half-- a half a night in the-- in a line for a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right away, we didn't have nothing to eat, because we had only the rations, what they gave us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a funny part that we-- you ask me about anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't walk on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
